			</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote18-20991_002_009"><a name="-20991_002_009">&nbsp;</a>
				<span class="label">18.</span>
				<p class="">V&eacute;ase <a href="http://lds.org/scriptures/nt/1-cor/2.11-14?lang=spa#10" target="_blank">1 Corintios 2:11–14</a>.</p>
			</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote19-20991_002_009"><a name="-20991_002_009">&nbsp;</a>
